==Chinese==
===[[Mandarin]]===
[[Pinyin]]: guāngmíng zhèngdà

===Idiom===
'''[[光明]][[正大]]'''

# high-principled; open and aboveboard; just and honorable; frank and righteous; without artifice
#: ''[[改革]][[是]][[公共]][[大眾]][[的]][[事]]，[[改革]][[是]]'''光明正大'''[[的]][[事]]，[[不能]][[只]][[在]][[少數]][[精英]][[貴族]][[中]][[討論]]，[[不能]][[靜悄悄]][[地]][[進行]]，[[更]][[不能]][[在]][[那裡]][[搞]][[什麼]][[暗箱操作]]。'' ([[Traditional Chinese]])
#: ''[[改革]][[是]][[公共]][[大众]][[的]][[事]]，[[改革]][[是]]'''光明正大'''[[的]][[事]]，[[不能]][[只]][[在]][[少数]][[精英]][[贵族]][[中]][[讨论]]，[[不能]][[静悄悄]][[地]][[进行]]，[[更]][[不能]][[在]][[那里]][[搞]][[什么]][[暗箱操作]]。'' ([[Simplified Chinese]])
#: ''Reform is a public affair for the masses.  Reform is an '''open and aboveboard''' affair.  It should not merely be discussed among a small number of the best and brightest of the aristocracy.  It should not be carried out in a "hush-hush" manner.  Last but not least, it should not be carried out somewhere as some kind of "black ops" thing.''

